name: Serie Tribute: 11 - Spider Man
description:
This new series has a collectible card format. It will make a tribute tour about superheroes and villains. A new creative venture of Roboto Inc. for its great collectors. Prototypes designed by Norma Xelda Jara. Let's have fun! 

First appearance: Amazing Fantasy #15 (August 10, 1962)
His abilities include strength, combat and intelligence, in addition to being able to produce and launch synthetic spider webs with the help of launchers attached to his wrists; climb, cling and move through walls and buildings; and perceive dangers and threats around him precognitively thanks to his "spider sense".
